OL,4,Cthe course
OL,6,FA horse racing fanatic celebrated his
OL,7,F104th birthday in fitting style with a
OL,8,Fparty at Catterick racecourse.
OL,10,FFrank Buttery, from , is a regular
OL,11,Fface on the racing circuit, having
OL,12,Fgone to his first event in 1942.
OL,14,FThe former race horse owner was
OL,15,Fserenaded with a birthday song before
OL,16,Fcutting a Victoria sponge.
OL,18,FIn a speech to the room, he said:
OL,19,F"It's a pleasure to be here and I'm
OL,20,Fgoing to make a promise that I'll be
OL,21,Fhere when I'm 105."
