OL,6,FFrank's first race day was special for
OL,7,Fmore reasons than one, being the same
OL,8,Fday he got married.
OL,10,F"We got married the same day and went
OL,11,Fto the races in the afternoon," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FAsked what he enjoys about racing, he
OL,15,Fsaid: "The people. The friendliness of
OL,16,Fit. Things like that. I like a bet.
OL,18,F"I've had four #5,000 bets in my life
OL,19,Fand three of them won."
